'''天主教阿卡普爾科總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Acapulcana}}；{{lang-es|Archidiócesis de Acapulco}}）是[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]一個[[總教區|總教區]]，位於[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[格雷羅州|格雷羅州]]南部，教座位於港口城市[[阿卡普爾科|阿卡普爾科]]。下轄三個教區。

==歷史==
1958年3月18日升為教區。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]|publisher=梵蒂岡出版社|date=1958年|volume=50|title=''Quo aptiori''|page=716|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2050%20%5B1958%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|access-date=2013-05-14|archive-date=2012-08-09|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69mL2kt3C?url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2050%20%5B1958%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>1983年2月10日升為總教區。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]|publisher=梵蒂岡出版社|date=1983年|volume=75|title=''Quo maius''|page=597|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2075%20%5B1983%5D%20I%20-%20ocr.pdf|access-date=2013-05-14|archive-date=2010-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100327065750/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2075%20%5B1983%5D%20I%20-%20ocr.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==現況==
2006年有教友2,940,000人，佔轄區總人口72.2%。總教區下轄七十八個堂區，有112名司鐸。

現任總主教為{{link-en|良保·貢薩萊斯-貢薩萊斯|Leopoldo González González}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 30.06.2017 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2017/06/30/0464/01036.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-09-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930134734/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2017/06/30/0464/01036.html |archivedate=2019-09-30 |language=it |date=2017-06-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-de|斐理伯·阿吉雷-弗蘭科|Felipe Aguirre Franco}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 07.06.2010 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/06/07/0378/00850.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-09-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930135219/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/06/07/0378/00850.html |archivedate=2019-09-30 |language=it |date=2010-06-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

